org.microtitan.diffusive.diffuser.restful.resources

Class ResultId

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.microtitan.diffusive.diffuser.restful.resources.ResultId

  • public class ResultId
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the components that make up the execute result ID used to retrieve results. The result ID is composed of the signature (DiffuserSignature) and the request ID generated and returned by the execute method. This class can be used to create and parse result IDs and get their component parts.
    Author:
    Robert Philipp
